    "body": "Removes the broad utility helpers used by generator naming and Neovim process startup.\r\n\r\nAPI metadata key mapping now uses System.Text.Json's snake_case policy. Generated C# identifiers keep a small generator-local snake_case mapping for the reverse direction, and start option flags use an explicit mapping instead of enum reflection.\r\n\r\nCloses #28 \r\n",
    "closed_at": "2026-06-15T11:36:13Z",
