            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "I know this is draft, but I just want to mention: if we are going to change the \"spelling\" to use underscores as in the original name, we should also just use the exact original name entirely:\n\n    del_augroup_by_name\n\nin other words, either fully adopt the \"platform style\" or fully don't.\n\n(personally, I think it's much better for everyone if the exact spelling is preserved instead of adopting \"platform style\", but we use platform style in the other clients, so that is a somewhat un-winnable battle....)",
